\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s Agel We  
\mt1 Yoęž‰n  
\mt2 E Saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we  
\ip Kalu bugoęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ we, Yoęž‰n. E Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ tili widoęž‰ kalu kugulaęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ nowoęž‰ e. E koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ ululaęž‰liabiki, moęž‰foęž‰s we tilidabu kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ agelemaęž‰ki, saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ wenamioęž‰, asuloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰labiki, asuloęž‰ dimaęž‰ki, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. To nowoęž‰ we, nioęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ ene insoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise domaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰ki, to we Yoęž‰naęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. To andeboęž‰ we, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ madali godeyaęž‰ man walasaęž‰lakiyoęž‰ widaęž‰lab aęž‰namioęž‰ moęž‰tilidabumaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to we aęž‰na alobana widoęž‰. Kalu aęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śGodeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa Yaęž‰su aęž‰noęž‰, kalu ni oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowanâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. To we hala saęž‰labiki, Yoęž‰n eyoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ to wenamioęž‰ moęž‰kudu hamanaęž‰ki, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\c 1  
\s1 To Melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.1\x*To melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ taminde amioęž‰ elen koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ dabu. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ninin siyaęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nili dagiyaęž‰yoęž‰ goloęž‰. To aęž‰namioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, to wekoęž‰ niliyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ walamaęž‰nigoęž‰l.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1.2 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.14\x*Melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kalule faęž‰laęž‰dotaęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ ninin baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na walasoęž‰loęž‰l. Tamin amioęž‰ e iya oęž‰liaęž‰ elen koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ niloęž‰ amioęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.  
\v 3 Gioęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰ ege domaęž‰ki, nililoęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ nililoęž‰ dabu aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰na walasoęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Insoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ ege dowaęž‰sen.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1.4 \xt Yoęž‰n 16.24\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ sagaloęž‰ nililoęž‰woęž‰ alan domaęž‰ki, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.   
\s1 Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ hoęž‰lena domaęž‰niki  
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 1.5 \xt 1Tim 6.16, Yaęž‰m 1.17\x*To we Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ malolabikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ dabu koęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Gode e hoęž‰len nafa maliloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ imilig nowoęž‰ e amioęž‰ mada aundoęž‰ma.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 2.4\x*Niliyoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śNe Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laki koęž‰sega, nioęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰liki, sololi oęž‰ngoęž‰wa siaęž‰lalega, to nililoęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nininoęž‰ madaliloęž‰ saęž‰lan kalu dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to man hendeleyoęž‰ niliyoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab.  
\v 7 Koęž‰sega Gode e, man nafale dimidaęž‰liki, maliloęž‰ hoęž‰lena aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ e dowoęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ dowalega, negeleboęž‰ ege domaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nili mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halaliki, nioęž‰ maliloęž‰ domaęž‰ib.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1.8 \xt Song 32.5, Sndn 28.13\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰, â€śNe mogagoęž‰woęž‰ aundoęž‰maâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ e mogagoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰dimidan aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰loęž‰le saęž‰lakigab koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ e amioęž‰ moęž‰daęž‰lab.  
\v 9 Nililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ fogaęž‰le saęž‰lalega, Gode eyoęž‰ enedoęž‰ to saefaęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ man nafa digaloęž‰ dimidaki, nili mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ gaęž‰lilaliki, nioęž‰ maliloęž‰ taęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\v 10 Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰, â€śNe mogagoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidanâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, to aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lan kalu aęž‰laęž‰li saęž‰laki gab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to man aęž‰noęž‰ kalu aęž‰maęž‰ asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ moęž‰daęž‰lab.   
\c 2  
\s1 Niloęž‰ asufaęž‰yoęž‰, Yaęž‰su  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2.1 \xt Hibu 7.25-26\x*Ni soęž‰wa i, gioęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidabenaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ to we gimoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Kalu imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidalega, niloęž‰ asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ aęž‰lab. Yaęž‰su Keliso, e mada digaloęž‰ kalu koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiloęž‰, Iyamoęž‰loęž‰ toloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰senoęž‰ e.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2.2 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.29, Kolo 1.20, 1Yoęž‰n 4.10\x*Mogagoęž‰ nililoęž‰woęž‰ dilaęž‰maęž‰ki, ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ walaki sowoęž‰. Eloęž‰ nanog di aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nikoęž‰ asufaęž‰ma, eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ amiloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale sab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ tambo asuwaęž‰taki goęž‰.   
\p
\v 3 Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lalega, nioęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ hendele asululi aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l.  
\v 4 Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naki, â€śNe Godeyoęž‰ hendele asuloęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ e madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lan kalu dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ e amioęž‰ moęž‰daęž‰lab.  
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 2.5-6 \xt Yoęž‰n 14.21,23\x*Koęž‰sega kalu abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lalega, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulan man aęž‰noęž‰ e amioęž‰ mada ililoęž‰. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ â€śNe Gode oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowoęž‰l,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, e Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ man dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leau dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Gode eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ i usamioęž‰ halaidoęž‰koęž‰ dofoęž‰melaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 2.7 \xt Yoęž‰n 13.34, 2Yoęž‰n 1.5-6\x*Ne mili, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l we, hoęž‰gima. To saefaęž‰ we, gioęž‰ hoęž‰gi moęž‰moęž‰da tilidaęž‰dakiloęž‰ dabu aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ waęž‰ka gimoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l.\f + \fr 2.7 \ft To hoęž‰gi saefaęž‰ we, tamin amioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ enedoęž‰ tili widan kalumoęž‰woęž‰ sioęž‰. Yoęž‰n 13.34,35 aęž‰namioęž‰ agelema.\f*  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2.8 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.9, Lom 13.12\x*Koęž‰sega to we hoęž‰gi aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ we. Man Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ gililoęž‰ dimidab oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, to saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hendeleloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ki soęž‰loęž‰l. Moęž‰woęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidan aęž‰noęž‰ sololi oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nabiki, hoęž‰lendeyoęž‰ tindaki soęž‰soęž‰idab.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 2.9 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 4.20\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰, â€śNe hoęž‰lena dofoęž‰loęž‰l,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰liki koęž‰sega eyoęž‰ tilidabu kalu nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ kele asulaki moęž‰beaęž‰lalega, e sololi aęž‰naka oęž‰ilikigab.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2.10 \xt Lom 14.13\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ ao nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰lalega, e hoęž‰lena dowab koęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e moęž‰hala hamanaęž‰ki, dinafa walamaęž‰ib.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2.11 \xt Yoęž‰n 12.35\x*Koęž‰sega kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ tilidabu kalu nolboęž‰woęž‰ kele asulaki moęž‰beaęž‰lalega, e sololi aęž‰naka iliki koęž‰loęž‰ e doęž‰bugu siaęž‰likigab. Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ siyoęž‰ koęž‰n oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e tog aęž‰na kudu hoęž‰noęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰dinafa asulab.   
\q1
\v 12 Soęž‰wa gioęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ wiya ilikiyoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ gili mogagoęž‰woęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰,  
\q2 to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.   
\q1
\v 13 Koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale giliyoęž‰, kalu taminde amiloęž‰ dowaęž‰i mioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, gioęž‰ digale asululi koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\q2 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.  
\q1 Kalukaęž‰isale asugoęž‰ hoęž‰gi nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu gi aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e tinioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰labiki,  
\q2 to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.  
\q1 Ni soęž‰wa i, Do Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ digale fanda asululi koęž‰loęž‰,  
\q2 to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.   
\q1
\v 14 Koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ giliyoęž‰, kalu taminde amiloęž‰ dowaęž‰i mioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, gioęž‰ digale asululi koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\q2 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.  
\q1 Kalukaęž‰isale asugoęž‰ hoęž‰gi nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu gi amioęž‰,  
\q2 halaidoęž‰woęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰,  
\q2 Godeyaęž‰ manoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ delen koęž‰loęž‰,  
\q2 mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e gili tinioęž‰.  
\q2 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ to we niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.   
\s1 Gioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ manoęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo  
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 2.15 \xt Lom 8.7\x*Gioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man we aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ daęž‰lab we asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰lalega, Do Gode asulan man aęž‰noęž‰ e amioęž‰ aundoęž‰moęž‰ daęž‰lab.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2.16 \xt Lom 13.14\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wiloęž‰ man dimidanoęž‰ we. Ini doęž‰moęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ asulan oęž‰liaęž‰, siyaęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ meselan oęž‰liaęž‰ kailan oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, henfeloęž‰ wemaęž‰ man. Man we Do Godeloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ma. Man aęž‰noęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ delenoęž‰ oęž‰m.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2.17 \xt Madi 7.21\x*Henfeloęž‰ we oęž‰liaęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidan aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo kelegaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nab koęž‰sega, kalukaęž‰isale Godeyaęž‰ to saefaęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ gisdoęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabi hagugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 2.18 \xt Madi 24.5,24, 2Yoęž‰n 1.7\x*Ni soęž‰wa i, henfeloęž‰ we elemaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowab. Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gisdoęž‰ diaęž‰lab kalu aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ tamina dabu. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gisdoęž‰ diaęž‰lab kalu modoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰ma faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ we koęž‰naęž‰ma elemaęž‰nigab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nioęž‰ asulab.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2.19 \xt Ilig 20.30\x*Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰, asuloęž‰ ililoęž‰woęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ imiligoęž‰ moęž‰dowabikiloęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰gane aęž‰noęž‰ nilinoęž‰ma. Iyoęž‰ nilinoęž‰ kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, ni oęž‰liaęž‰ka oęž‰domabe. Koęž‰sega iliyoęž‰ nioęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰gane koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ hendele nilinoęž‰ma aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 2.20 \xt 1Kol 2.15, 2Kol 1.21, 2Yoęž‰n 1.2\x*Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ma. Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ gimoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ tambo asululi koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 21 Niloęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l we, gioęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ moęž‰asuloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likima. Gioęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰labiki, niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Moęž‰woęž‰ to hendele us amioęž‰ madali towoęž‰ moęž‰alab.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 2.22 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 4.3, 2Yoęž‰n 1.7\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śYaęž‰su e, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo gasilimaęž‰kiloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰, emakaęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰lalega, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ e madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lanoęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Insoęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ gola baęž‰daki, kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ gis diab.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 2.23 \xt Yoęž‰n 5.23, 1Yoęž‰n 4.15, 5.1\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ Insoęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ gola baęž‰dalega, Iya Gode oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ gab. Kalu abeyoęž‰ Insoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amioęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Iya Gode amioęž‰ e dowakigab.  
\v 24 Tamin amiloęž‰ to gililoęž‰ dabu aęž‰noęž‰, gili asuloęž‰ amioęž‰ dinafa halale asulufoęž‰lubi. To aęž‰noęž‰ gili asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ asulufoęž‰lalega, Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Insoęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ib.  
\v 25 Tamin amioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ dinali saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śmelaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰ dimioęž‰lâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰.   
\p
\v 26 Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ hala tililiaęž‰ haęž‰nab koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hagugaki to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 2.27 \xt Yoęž‰n 16.13\x*Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ di koęž‰loęž‰, e gi oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰walamaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulumaęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mama aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo ami gimoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ Mama aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ towoęž‰ halayoęž‰ moęž‰widaki, to hendeleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ Mama eloęž‰ widab au, Yaęž‰su e oęž‰liaęž‰ kegene dowaęž‰bi.   
\s1 Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa  
\p
\v 28 Ni soęž‰wa i, gioęž‰ Godeya ogaęž‰ditaęž‰gaęž‰ dofoęž‰melea. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ yalikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ moęž‰sendelowaki, halaidoęž‰ kagamaęž‰ib.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 2.29 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 3.10\x*Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ manoęž‰ digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ giliyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale manoęž‰ digaloęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab i aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa dowakaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰, giliyoęž‰ asulumaęž‰ib.   
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3.1 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.12-13, 16.3\x*Wai! Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ ene soęž‰wakaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰safoęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ hendele Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa koęž‰loęž‰lab. Henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Do Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰fanda asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, iliyoęž‰ nioęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰fanda asulab.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3.2 \xt 2Kol 3.18\x*Ne mili, nioęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa dowab. Gode eyoęž‰ tif amioęž‰ nioęž‰ we oęž‰ngoęž‰ domaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, kalab amioęž‰ oęž‰semoęž‰widoęž‰. Koęž‰sega Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, e wengoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ hendele misioęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ e oęž‰ngoęž‰ka domaęž‰ib.  
\v 3 Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hendele faęž‰laęž‰domabesaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ yasilaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ene asuloęž‰ amioęž‰ mogagoęž‰ aęž‰dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ eletaęž‰gaęž‰, e Yaęž‰su oęž‰ngoęž‰ goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 4 Mogagoęž‰ dimidan man oęž‰liaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰sab man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ imiloęž‰ dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰loęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰saęž‰lab.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3.5 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.29, 1Bid 2.22-24, 1Yoęž‰n 2.2\x*Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ nili mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ dilaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nioęž‰ asuloęž‰. Mogagoęž‰ imilise nowoęž‰ e amioęž‰ aundoęž‰ma.  
\v 6 Kalu abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su e oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu abeyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ene asuloęž‰ amioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰daki, e moęž‰fanda asulab.   
\p
\v 7 Ni soęž‰wa i, kalu imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ dikili saęž‰labenaęž‰ki, gioęž‰ dinafa yasi dowaęž‰bi! Yaęž‰su Keliso e digaloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e hendele digaloęž‰, Yaęž‰su e oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3.8 \xt Yoęž‰n 8.44\x*Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yoęž‰ tamina aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰loęž‰, mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰i yaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ilikigab. Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wayoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰loęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ bidilaęž‰maęž‰ni mioęž‰.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3.9 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 5.18\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa dowab aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ eya dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰sen. E Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa koęž‰loęž‰, mogagoęž‰woęž‰ mada moęž‰dimidaęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 10 Ge Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa oęž‰liaęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ insoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ ele baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wama. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰disaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, e Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wama.   
\s1 Tilidabu kalu nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi  
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 3.11 \xt Yoęž‰n 13.34\x*Nioęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lubi aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ tamina dabu.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 4.8\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ Kaęž‰in e oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ dowaęž‰soęž‰bo. E mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ insoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ene aowoęž‰ soęž‰noęž‰. Eloęž‰ soęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Kaęž‰in e man mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len. Aęž‰ibol e man digaloęž‰ dimidaęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰, Kaęž‰inaęž‰yoęž‰ ene aowoęž‰ aęž‰na sana sowoęž‰.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3.13 \xt Yoęž‰n 5.18-19\x*Henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰woęž‰ kele asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰bealikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ iligaęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3.14 \xt Yoęž‰n 5.24\x*Tamin amioęž‰ nioęž‰ somaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰ elen koęž‰sega nioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ma tiginitaęž‰gaęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ usa faęž‰laęž‰dofoęž‰loęž‰l. Niliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ niliyoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale no oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen. Kalu abeyoęž‰ nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰disaęž‰lalega, e somaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3.15 \xt Kala 21.8\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ ene ao nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ kele asulakiloęž‰ moęž‰beaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, kalu sana sowanoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu sana sowan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ e amioęž‰ moęž‰dofoęž‰likigab, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ asuloęž‰.\f + \fr 3.15 \ft Kalu nowoęž‰mboęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰beaęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰ kalu sana sowab oęž‰liaęž‰ man dimidan aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ imilise oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ baęž‰dab.\f* \fig Giyoęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lubi.|alt="Eating together at a table" src="62_1Jn_03_03_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="3.11" \fig*   
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 3.16 \xt Yoęž‰n 13.1, Gala 1.4\x*Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ ni asulakiloęž‰, ene melaęž‰noęž‰ walaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ao nowoęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰loęž‰ nao nowoęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, nili melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰walaęž‰maęž‰niki.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3.17 \xt Lo 15.7\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ e kelegoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li deliki, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰nofolalega, Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ e amioęž‰ aundoęž‰ma.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3.18 \xt Yaęž‰m 2.15-16\x*Ni soęž‰wa i, giliyoęž‰ to mosowaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ megoęž‰faęž‰yoęž‰ madaliyoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega kalu nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ hendele nofolakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki to sioęž‰ aumboęž‰, nanogoęž‰ hendele dagiyaęž‰yoęž‰ dimidaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 19-20 Niliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰la ilikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ moęž‰sendelowaki haęž‰saka domaęž‰noęž‰. Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene asuloęž‰ nafale aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nili asuloęž‰woęž‰ tininilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ e asululi koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 21-22 \x - \xo 3.21-22 \xt Hibu 4.16\x*Ne mili, asuloęž‰ ninidoęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰sendelo alitalega, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ tagioęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, Godemoęž‰loęž‰ dabu baęž‰dab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ hendele dimiaęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naki, man eloęž‰ asulab aumboęž‰ dimidaęž‰i yaęž‰len.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 3.23 \xt Yoęž‰n 6.29, 13.34\x*Godeyaęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ we. Nioęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa, Yaęž‰su Kelisowa tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kalu nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi. Eloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰m koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 3.24 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 4.13\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ eloęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰noęž‰, e Godeya dowab koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eloęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dowab. Godeyoęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nioęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki, Godeyaęž‰ Mama nimoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰lab.   
\c 4  
\s1 To widaboęž‰ alobana baęž‰daęž‰bi  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 4.1 \xt Madi 7.15, 1Tes 5.21, 1Yoęž‰n 2.18, 2Yoęž‰n 1.7\x*Ne mili, madaliloęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kaluwoęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ henfeloęž‰ amioęž‰ dalale siliki manoęž‰ widaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ manoęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, â€śGodeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ ne amioęž‰ dowoęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ widab aęž‰noęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega e Godeyaęž‰ Mamaleyaęž‰ saęž‰labaęž‰le aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ alobana baęž‰daęž‰bi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4.2 \xt 1Kol 12.3\x*To we Godeyaęž‰ Mamaleyaęž‰ gab aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ alobana asulumaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Kalu abeyoęž‰ â€śYaęž‰su Keliso e hende kalule mioęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ kalu e amioęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 2.18\x*Koęž‰sega kalu abeyoęž‰ â€śYaęž‰su e kalulemaâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, kalu aęž‰namioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma koęž‰loęž‰, e Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis diakigab. Man aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ sioęž‰woęž‰ gioęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ oęž‰ma henfeloęž‰ wena faęž‰laęž‰dotaęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 4.4 \xt Madi 12.29, 1Yoęž‰n 5.4-5\x*Ni soęž‰wa i, gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enoęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ madaliloęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kalu aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰lika tininimaęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode gi oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ e halaidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wiloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ tinioęž‰.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4.5 \xt Yoęž‰n 8.47, 15.19\x*Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wena aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ililoęž‰ man widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wiloęž‰ dimidan manoęž‰ oęž‰m. Henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ililoęž‰ man widab aęž‰noęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰lab.  
\v 6 Koęž‰sega nioęž‰ Godeloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ Godeloęž‰ alan asuloęž‰ i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nililoęž‰ to widaboęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰lab. Kalu abeyoęž‰ Godeloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰mioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nililoęž‰ to widaboęž‰ moęž‰tilidaęž‰daęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰ to hendele oęž‰liaęž‰ madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lan mama aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, niliyoęž‰ dinafa alobana baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asulumaęž‰noęž‰.   
\s1 Haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ Gode E  
\p
\v 7 Ne mili, negeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰niki. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ Godeloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰. Kalu nolboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ disaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ tambo Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa koęž‰loęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 8 Kalu nol oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ Gode e. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰disaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, eyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 4.9 \xt Yoęž‰n 3.16\x*Gode eyoęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰ aęž‰lakiloęž‰ nimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰woęž‰ we. Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ nanog dimidoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, nioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ eya dimaęž‰ki, Gode eyoęž‰ ene Insoęž‰ imiligoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wena iligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4.10 \xt Lom 5.8-10, 1Yoęž‰n 2.2\x*Hendele haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰ aęž‰lakiloęž‰ dimidanoęž‰ we. Godemoęž‰woęž‰ nili koęž‰le haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰ma. Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ mada haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ene Soęž‰wayaęž‰yoęž‰ nili mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dilaęž‰maęž‰ki iligaęž‰foęž‰.   
\p
\v 11 Ne mili, Gode eyoęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niliyoęž‰loęž‰ negeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰disaęž‰maęž‰niki.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4.12 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.18\x*Kalukaęž‰isale imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ misioęž‰ mada moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰. Koęž‰sega niliyoęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰lalega, Godeyoęž‰ ni usa dofoęž‰liki, Gode eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ ni usamioęž‰ halaidoęž‰koęž‰ dofoęž‰melaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 4.13 \xt 2Kol 1.22, 1Yoęž‰n 3.24\x*Gode e ni oęž‰liaęž‰ dowab aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰loęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰loęž‰l. Niliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ asuloęž‰l we, Gode eyoęž‰ ene Mamayoęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimi.  
\v 14 Gode eyoęž‰ ene Soęž‰wayoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ eloęž‰ amiloęž‰ ane aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasilimaęž‰ki iligaęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰noęž‰ niliyoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nolboęž‰woęž‰ kalaba widaęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 15 Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su e, hendele Godeyaęž‰ Soęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ kalab amiloęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyoęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰ dowab aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ dowab.  
\v 16 Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰, nioęž‰ hendele asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu. Kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ Gode e. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, Gode eloęž‰ e amioęž‰ dofoęž‰lab.  
\v 17 Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ gab aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ ni amioęž‰ halaidoęž‰koęž‰ dofoęž‰lab. Nioęž‰ hen wena oęž‰silikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰ngoęž‰ dofoęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleloęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab aęž‰namioęž‰, nioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ kagayaki moęž‰tagimaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 18 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ disaęž‰lab kalu aęž‰noęž‰ e moęž‰tagilan. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ e amiloęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dofoęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ tagilan e amiloęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰ dilaęž‰. Kaluloęž‰ tagilab aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we. Kaluwaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidab amiloęž‰ waęž‰l miaęž‰ib aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulaki tagilab. Kalu abeyoęž‰ e amioęž‰ tagioęž‰ dowab aęž‰noęž‰, Gode eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ e amioęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dofoęž‰likigab.  
\v 19 Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ tamina disaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niliyoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 20 Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ â€śNe Godemoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laki koęž‰sega, ene ao ado nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ kele asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰beaęž‰lalega, e madali dikili saęž‰laęž‰lab. Moęž‰woęž‰ eyoęž‰ ao ado iyoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰likiyoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰disaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰ eyoęž‰ Gode misiloęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰dan oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ mada moęž‰disaęž‰maęž‰ib.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 4.21 \xt Mak 12.29-31\x*Gode eloęž‰ nimoęž‰loęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ we. Kalu abeyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ disaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ene ao nolboęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka disaęž‰laęž‰bi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ manoęž‰ tinioęž‰  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 5.1 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 4.15\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su e Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰, e Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa. Kalu abeyoęž‰ Domoęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ene soęž‰wa nolboęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰lab.  
\v 2 Nioęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ene to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu haęž‰nalega, man nilidoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, niliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wa nolboęž‰woęž‰ mada hendele haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widakigab.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 5.3 \xt Yoęž‰n 14.15,23-24\x*Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to saefaęž‰yoęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰namioęž‰, nioęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakigab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to eloęž‰ saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ma.  
\v 4 Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man we tininilab. Nililoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ manoęž‰ tininilab.  
\v 5 Henfeloęž‰ man we, kalu oęž‰boęž‰ngoęž‰maęž‰ tinianoęž‰? Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su e Godeyaęž‰ Soęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ tili asulab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ amiloęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ koęž‰liloęž‰ daęž‰lab we eka tininilab.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 5.6 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.29-34\x*Yaęž‰su Keliso e Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wiloęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, hoęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ widoęž‰. Hoęž‰n aęž‰maęž‰ka widoęž‰ma. Hoęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ widoęž‰.\f + \fr 5.6 \ft Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wiloęž‰ mioęž‰ amioęž‰, e hoęž‰n amioęž‰ toęž‰loloęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ene hoęž‰boęž‰woęž‰ i malana tulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su e Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki widaki goęž‰.\f* Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ fanda widaęž‰sen.  
\v 7 Yaęž‰su e Godeyaęž‰ Soęž‰walekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ otalen wemaęž‰ widab.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 5.8 \xt Yoęž‰n 15.26\x*Mamayoęž‰, hoęž‰noęž‰, hoęž‰boęž‰woęž‰ kelegoęž‰ otalen aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, nimoęž‰woęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise widaęž‰lab.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5.9 \xt Yoęž‰n 5.32-37\x*Kaluwaęž‰ siyaęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, niliyoęž‰ tili daęž‰daęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ tininilab koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ mada tilidaęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰. Moęž‰woęž‰ e Gode koęž‰loęž‰ to eloęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ ene Soęž‰wayoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ fanda sioęž‰.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5.10 \xt Yoęž‰n 5.36-40\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Soęž‰wa amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab i aęž‰namioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ hendelekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ ili asuloęž‰ amioęž‰ ti ali koęž‰loęž‰lab. Koęž‰sega kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wayoęž‰ weloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰tilidaęž‰dab koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ madali toloęž‰ saęž‰lan aęž‰lakigab.  
\v 11 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nimoęž‰loęž‰ to sioęž‰woęž‰ we. Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ene Soęž‰waleya dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5.12 \xt Yoęž‰n 3.36\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Insoęž‰le amiloęž‰ dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ taęž‰li sab. Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Insoęž‰le amiloęž‰ moęž‰dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰taęž‰li sab. \fig Yaęž‰su e Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, hoęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ widoęž‰.|alt="Close-up of Jesus on cross" src="42_Lk_23_33_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="5.6" \fig*   
\s1 Nioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ di aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰niki  
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 5.13 \xt Yoęž‰n 20.31\x*Giliyoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰ma di aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ki, Godeyaęž‰ Soęž‰wa amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰woęž‰ to we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5.14 \xt Yoęž‰n 14.13-14, 1Yoęž‰n 3.21-22\x*Nili asuloęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, kelegoęž‰ noloęž‰ dabu baęž‰dalega, eyoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ hendele dimidamaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ tagioęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, e aniba domaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 15 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ nililoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ hendele daęž‰dab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ niliyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, emoęž‰loęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ niliyoęž‰ oęž‰ma dioęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰asulab.   
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 5.16 \xt Madi 12.31\x*Gioęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nomaęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, mogagoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e somaęž‰noęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dowoęž‰lalega, giliyoęž‰ e asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalu mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib. Man mogagoęž‰ nol somaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰nan aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰lab, koęž‰sega giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dulugu sama aęž‰laęž‰li soęž‰loęž‰ba.  
\v 17 Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ digaloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ noloęž‰ somaęž‰noęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰tililiaęž‰ haęž‰nan koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 5.18 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 3.9\x*Kalukaęž‰isale Godeyaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, mogagoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰melaęž‰ib. Kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa Yaęž‰suwaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰laliki, mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ moęž‰gomaęž‰ib.  
\v 19 Nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enenoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ henfeloęž‰ we tambo mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ eyoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nioęž‰ asuloęž‰.  
\v 20 Niliyoęž‰ Gode hendele aęž‰noęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wayoęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nimoęž‰woęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ dimi. Nioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa oęž‰liaęž‰ ege dofoęž‰loęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰ Gode hendele e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ ege dofoęž‰loęž‰l. E Gode hendele aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ e.  
\v 21 Ni soęž‰wa i, madali gode amioęž‰ ege dowabenaęž‰ki, gioęž‰ dinafa dowaęž‰biyoęž‰!   